      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 750ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
