    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
