    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grind the <strong>chopped basil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> to form a paste</p><p>Add 3-4 tbsp <strong>olive oil </strong>or enough to loosen and mix well – this is your <strong>basil oil</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don't have a pestle & mortar, chop the basil leaves very finely and mix with salt and olive oil</p>",
